  "response": "The best oven mitts depend on personal preference, but some highly-rated options include:\n\n1. Silicone Oven Mitts\n- Heat resistant up to 500\u00b0F\n- Waterproof and easy to clean\n- Good grip\n- Brands like OXO and GEEKHOM are popular\n\n2. Cotton Quilted Mitts\n- Traditional style\n- Comfortable and lightweight\n- Good for moderate heat\n- Brands like Cuisinart and KitchenAid make quality options\n\n3. Neoprene Mitts\n- Flexible and comfortable\n- Good heat resistance\n- Often longer for more arm protection\n- DexShell and HOMWE make well-reviewed versions\n\n4. Professional Grade Mitts\n- Extra thick\n- Highest heat resistance\n- Often used in commercial kitchens\n- Brands like San Jamar and Rapicca are top choices\n\nFactors to consider:\n- Heat resistance\n- Grip\n- Length of protection\n- Comfort\n- Ease of cleaning\n\nUltimately, the best mitt depends on your specific cooking needs and personal comfort.",
